---
// the-wonders-of-the-universe.astro
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="The Wonders of the Universe | Cosmic Astro">
  <article class="blog-post">
    <h1>The Wonders of the Universe</h1>
    <p>The universe is an endless canvas of mysteries and beauty. From sprawling galaxies to luminous nebulae, each celestial body tells a story of creation and wonder.</p>
    <p>Galaxies swirl in cosmic dances, and the remnants of exploded stars paint the sky with vibrant hues. When we gaze into the night, we see light that has traveled millions of years, connecting us to an ancient past.</p>
    <p>Join me as I explore the phenomena that make our universe truly awe-inspiring.</p>
  </article>
</Layout>

<style>
  .blog-post {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 2rem auto;
    padding: 2rem;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    border-radius: 8px;
    color: var(--text-color);
  }
  .blog-post h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .blog-post p {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
</style>
